title: Add congruent and 2 related datasets for teaching
checking data compatibility re: spdep
body: These changes clean some datasets, permit spdep to hand off data storage to spData, and provide the basis for the sf/spdep nb_sf vignette about constructing neighbours. Once this reaches CRAN, (check version numbers), I'll be able to start releasing spdep, start transiting spdep to github/r-spatial, and warning downstream package maintainers who expect datasets to be carried by spdep (there may be a lot). Have used roxygen2::roxygenize("spData") to regenerate man/ etc.
